Modifications in this fork include:
- A-stock (China mainland) data layer using mootdx, Tencent Finance, and akshare
- Three new A-stock specific analyst agents (Policy, Hot Money, Lockup)
- A-stock trading constraints (T+1, price limits, lot sizes) in Trader and PM
- Chinese language output support
- CSI 300 benchmark for alpha calculation (replacing SPY)
- Various prompt and pipeline adaptations for A-share market specifics

See the upstream CHANGES_FROM_UPSTREAM.md for the full list of modifications.
